     fhir:documentation [ fhir:v "Subject for which the gaps in care report will be created is provided as a Group resource. Subjects provided in this parameter SHALL match the subjectType of the measure being evaluated.  (e.g. if the Measure.group.subjectType is Patient, the subject SHALL be a reference to a Patient or a Group of Patients). If no subject is provided, what subjects are evaluated is up to the server. This parameter cannot be used with the subject parameter." ] ;
